  "text": "Power transfer efficiency In this study, we focus on allocating constant total energy E among sensors. To achieve this goal, in practice, more energy than E will be transferred by the charger due to efficiency problems. Although there has been researches aiming at promoting power transfer efficiency [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ), more researches are still required.",
